messages.message: Is there a way to see what's inside the local database in crafting? For some context, on our laptop, localhost would use the dogfood db when we made changes through the AIHub website. However, I'm wondering if it's the same on crafting and if not, how to set up the connection (and if there's some useful extensions to install like oracle sql developer extension: https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=Oracle.sql-developer)
